description:
cmd/5c, cmd/5g, cmd/5l: enable 8 more floating point registers
   To my best knowledge, ARM VFP supports at least 16 floating point
registers.
   The old code only enabled F0 to F7, I think it's because old FPA has
only 8 registers.
   Note: our software floating point emulator already supports this.

**WIP**: this CL alone won't give much benefit.
